===Etymology===
Named by its discoverer {{w|Paul Emile Lecoq de Boisbaudran|Lecoq}}, after {{etyl|la|en}} {{m|la|Gallia||Gaul}}. It was claimed that Lecoq had named the element after himself, since {{m|la|gallus}} is the Latin translation of the French ''le {{m|fr|coq}}'', but Lecoq denied this in an article of 1877.

